  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectingFlight
    Connecting flight
    Filter
    Given an list of all possible flights from source airport to destination airport, filter these list by specifying class of seat, by specifying number of stops, and by specifying time window
    FilterConnectingFlights
    Filter list of connecting flights, choose the first 10 connecting flights in the list if the list size is larger than 10
    FilterTest
    Test Filter.java
    manageLineData
    Deal with related data of flights from one airport to another (direct flights and connecting flights), these data including total price, total flight duration, taking off time, landing time, flight detail of each leg, lay-over time of each leg
    manageLineDataTest
    Test manageLineData.java
    Search
    Search the target flight
    SearchDoSearchTest
    Test the most important function do search
    SearchFindFlightsOnDayTest
    Test for searching flight of some specific dates
    SortByDuration
    Sort Flights according to fly duration (shorter to longer)
    SortByLandingTime
    Sort Flights according to landing time (earlier to later)
    SortByPrice
    Sort Flights according to price (lower to higher)
    SortByTakeoffTime
    Sort Flights according to take off time (earlier to later)
    SortConnectingFlights
    sort connecting flights according to their distance attribute(total distance from departing airport and to destination airport
    SortTest
    Test various Sort classes
